comment: 10/4/14 - Bottled today. Floccuation was VERY high, basically formed a nice solid cake on the bottom of the fermenter. Only was able to get 23 bottles (out of an expected 24), but there was a little in the 24th bottle that I tried. Tasted slightly sweet, so I'm hoping it completely fermented. Will write comments back on the 11th when a week has passed.
